---
title: Spiced Chicken & Tandoori Roasted Pumpkin with Salad & Cucumber Raita
description: Sure, we’ve all heard of tandoori chicken, but this tandoori roasted pumpkin is the game-changer we've been salivating for. Paired with lightly spiced chicken thighs and a cucumber raita to cool things down, this is a quirky take on an Indian classic done right.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-chicken-tandoori-pumpkin-a482caa2.jpg
